Hello,
You must still connected...for permit others to D/L it!!!

Seeding with BITCOMET (must be same for others..)
Hit 'Maker'. This brings up the make torrent gui. 
Fill in the fields. 
If it's just one file, point to that file. 
If more than one file, click 'Directory (Multi-files)' and point to that 
directory. 
Fill in the tracker address (you need a tracker which you can get 
from the web site that's hosting the torrent). 
Select an output directory and give a name for the .torrent file. 
Hit O.K. 
(you may also drap directory/file into bitcomet. That dialog above will show up.) 
Upload your .torrent file to the website. 
Start the seeding task.
